    \[
      q_{\rm rot}
      =\frac{298.15}{2\times0.5615}
      =265.5\,.
    \]
4.  The molar rotational free energy is
    \[
      G_{\rm rot}
      =-RT\ln q_{\rm rot}
      =-(8.31446\;\mathrm{J\,mol^{-1}K^{-1}})(298.15\;\mathrm K)\ln(265.5)
      =-1.383\times10^{4}\;\mathrm{J\,mol^{-1}}
